        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ],
          "text": "1. Early America and Native Civilizations"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Describe the major Native American civilizations that existed in America before the arrival of Europeans. Explain their way of life, culture, and contributions to early American society."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null,
        "level": 3
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ],
          "text": "2. European Exploration and Colonization"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Explain the reasons why European nations explored and colonized America. Discuss the effects of colonization on Native Americans and early settlers."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null,
        "level": 3
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ],
          "text": "3. The American Revolution"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Discuss the main causes of the American Revolution. Explain how the colonies gained independence from British rule and the importance of this event in world history."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null,
        "level": 3
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ],
          "text": "4. Slavery and the Civil War"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Explain the role of slavery in American history and how it led to the Civil War. Discuss the major outcomes of the war and how it changed the nation."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null,
        "level": 3
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ],
          "text": "5. America’s Growth into a World Power"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Describe how America developed into a global power during the 19th and 20th centuries. Include major events, inventions, wars, and social changes that contributed to this growth."
        }
      ]
    }
